{"tid":1678222,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"講得白啲，而家香港最需要嘅係朝早十八區開花，唔係嘅話準時返工返學","createTime":"2019-10-27T14:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T18:58:21.000Z","uid":219269,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0beca82b6fbc4791667faab03a79b6bab61bc8d4","tid":1678222,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"如果早上進行抗爭，將會打破現時運動樽頸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644571</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好多人仲唔明<br />\n有咩可以響下面問<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅抗爭出招太單調<br />\n局限埋自己響週末<br />\n<br />\n唔好再問有咩可以突破<br />\n呢個就係突破點<br />\n<br />\n建議勇武手足響每朝最人多嘅時候出手<br />\n安全好多又可以達到目的<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>和理返工只係朝早開花嘅下位贋品</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b7dfee25cbaa0e4765d5c11772f8546cf9d33d30","tid":1678222,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:21:05.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"8c8a8022fa3c927bdc1f8e64df28269dc7094e10","tid":1678222,"uid":219269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"如果唔可以早起嘅<br />\n當我冇講過"},{"pid":"47d5054e1d9b6666ce4742a3cb659c5462c376a1","tid":1678222,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<br />\n鐘庭耀為今次運動發起全港性民調，追蹤長期民意<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4VuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=a853b68a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"e02259be30c8c079762f0d5c3c498f709e64510f","tid":1678222,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":